      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "that is partly true. findFirst() has following rule: &quot;When there is no encounter order it returns any element from the Stream.&quot; -&gt; so if your filter does not return the matched element, findFirst() will return the first one (except the stream is empty beforehand)"
    } ],
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 6340208,
      "reputation" : 49833,
      "user_id" : 4922375,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "accept_rate" : 96,
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/0754896d1b70cf0e3695f439775dfffe?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG&f=y&so-version=2",
