    "answer_id" : 59465615,
    "question_id" : 38725445,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>my solution was to check it this way</p>\n\n<pre><code>if(item.isPresent()){\n  item.get().setId(\"1q2w3e4r5t6y\")\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
    "comments" : [ {
      "owner" : {
        "account_id" : 4226254,
