    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Optional was created so code could after all these decades, finally start <strong><em>avoiding</em></strong> null.</p>\n\n<p>Remove the .get(), return the Optional itself and make the calling code deal with it appropriately (just as it would have to do in the case you'd be returning null).</p>\n"
